类 DFAM

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.com.hiocde.DFAM

  • public class DFAM
extends java.lang.Object
    DFAM is a definite finite automata which is used for identifying token by 3-type grammar definition.
    作者:
    Hmqi
    另请参阅:
    State, ItemsCluster

      • main

        public static void main(java.lang.String[] args)
        main is the entry of the whole program.it needs three params from console.
        参数:
        args - args[0] --- regular grammar file path
        args[1] --- source text file path | start lexical analysis
        args[2] --- type-2 grammar file path | start phasing

      • init

        public void init(java.lang.String gpath)
        init is a initial function used for constructing NFA according to regular grammar then converting to DFA
        参数:
        gpath - lexical file path , must be regular grammar.

      • run

        public java.lang.String run(java.lang.String text_path)
        Running my DFAM , it turns source text into token stream.
        参数:
        text_path - source text file path.
        返回:
        tokens file path with the same directory of source text.
